  <h1>üõçÔ∏è Product Management REST API</h1>
  <p>This is a simple Spring Boot REST API for managing products. It supports CRUD operations and uses an H2 in-memory database, making it lightweight and ideal for development or demonstration purposes.</p>

  <h2>üöÄ Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Add new products with validation</li>
    <li>Fetch all products or by name</li>
    <li>Update product details</li>
    <li>Delete a product by name</li>
    <li>Input validation and exception handling</li>
    <li>In-memory H2 database (no setup needed)</li>
    <li>RESTful endpoints</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>üßæ Product Structure</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Field</th><th>Type</th><th>Constraints</th></tr>
    <tr><td><code>id</code></td><td>Long</td><td>Auto-generated</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>name</code></td><td>String</td><td>Required, not blank</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>description</code></td><td>String</td><td>4‚Äì255 characters</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>price</code></td><td>Double</td><td>Must be positive, not null</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>üì¨ API Endpoints</h2>
  <p>Base URL: <code>/api</code></p>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Method</th><th>Endpoint</th><th>Description</th></tr>
    <tr><td>GET</td><td><code>/all</code></td><td>Get all products</td></tr>
    <tr><td>GET</td><td><code>/?name=productName</code></td><td>Get product by name</td></tr>
    <tr><td>POST</td><td><code>/createProduct</code></td><td>Create a new product</td></tr>
    <tr><td>PUT</td><td><code>/updateProduct?name=productName</code></td><td>Update product by name</td></tr>
    <tr><td>DELETE</td><td><code>/deleteProduct?name=productName</code></td><td>Delete product by name</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>üõ†Ô∏è Example: Create a Product</h2>
  <p><strong>POST</strong> <code>/api/createProduct</code></p>
  <pre>{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "description": "A powerful gaming laptop",
  "price": 1200.0
}</pre>

  <h2>‚ö†Ô∏è Error Handling</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Validation errors (e.g. blank name, invalid price)</li>
    <li>Duplicate product names</li>
    <li>Product not found</li>
    <li>General server exceptions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>üß™ H2 Database Console</h2>
  <p>Access at: <a href="http://localhost:8080/h2-console">http://localhost:8080/h2-console</a></p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>JDBC URL</strong>: <code>jdbc:h2:mem:testdb</code></li>
    <li><strong>Username</strong>: <code>sa</code></li>
    <li><strong>Password</strong>: (leave blank)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>üìö Technologies Used</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Java 17+</li>
    <li>Spring Boot</li>
    <li>Spring Data JPA</li>
    <li>H2 In-memory database</li>
    <li>REST API principles</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>üõ°Ô∏è Security Note</h2>
  <p>This project is meant for development and learning. Avoid exposing the H2 console in public or production environments.</p>

